we can now move on to the rest of america she said urging 
people to complete their census forms and send them back promptly 
nearly 85 million census forms already have been trucked to bulk 
distribution centers of the us postal service they will go into 
the hands of letter carriers friday for delivery to homes 
nationwide 
forms will be stuffed in mailboxes or held with other mail but 
they will not be forwarded to people who have moved 
people who havent received a form by april 2 are being asked to 
