court of criminal appeals ruled that luan van hoang had been 
illegally sentenced to an adult prison 
the prosecutors strategy potentially could expose the teenager 
to three life sentences in prison 
i think its appropriate that he be held accountable whether 
its in juvenile court or felony adult court for the action he 
