or what might happen to the works which include paintings by 
rembrandt vermeer degas and manet 
if there is no ransom demand in the coming days one could 
suppose the paintings are with someone she said referring to a 
theft by contract but we can imagine everything works of such 
value are unsalable 
europe leads the world in stolen art works with italy then 
