fasanella 87 who retired in october after logging 68 years 
243 days as a cabby was told last week by the guinness book of 
world records that he is the worlds longest licensed taxi driver 
breaking the previous mark by more than a decade 
the former recordholder francis edward kenyon of manchester 
england held his taxi license 57 yearsplus from 1924 to 1981 
