lord rothschild the millionaire banker and 
decorated world war ii intelligence agent died tuesday at age 79 
his family declined to disclose the cause of death 
lord rothschild was born nathaniel mayer victor rothschild into 
a famous family of germanjewish coin collectors who founded a 
banking dynasty 
he succeeded his uncle as the 3rd baron rothschild in 1937 
taking his seat in the house of lords the nonelected upper 
chamber of parliament as a member of the labor party 
during world war ii rothschild served as a senior officer with 
mi5 the british counterespionage service 
responding to what he said were years of innuendo in the press 
rothschild wrote the daily telegraph in 1986 urging mi5 to state 
publicly that it had unequivocal evidence disproving rumors 
that he was the fifth man in the infamous soviet spy ring 
formed by guy burgess kim philby donald maclean and anthony blunt 
prime minister margaret thatcher said the government had no 
evidence that rothschild was ever a soviet agent 
