your chances of getting a telephoned tax 
question answered correctly by the irs are considerably better this 
year but you will have more difficulty getting your call answered 
at all auditors said today 
this year irs assistors have responded accurately to 78 
percent of our taxlaw questions compared to 66 percent for the 
