missiles if any were transfered before or after the signing of 
the intermediate nuclear forces or inf treaty in december 1987 
if the weapons were transferred before the treaty was signed by 
former president reagan and soviet president mikhail s gorbachev 
they are not covered by the pact boucher said 
if they were transferred after it was signed the transfer 
violates the treaty he said 
