here are some facts about ltryptophan dietary 
supplements which have been linked to a blood disorder called 
eosinophiliamyalgia syndrome or ems 
symptoms breathing difficulties cough skin rashes of varying 
severity swelling of the extremities joint pain muscle weakness 
and fever in some instances there might be signs of congestive 
heart failure and paralysis 
uses of ltryptophan insomnia premenstrual syndrome stress 
reduction appetite control depression and others 
manufacturers two largest are p leiner nutritional products 
corp in torrance calif and pharmavite corp in arleta calif 
according to the council for responsible nutrition both the fda 
and an official at p leiner said a list of brand names could not 
be provided because hundreds of products were invovled large 
manufacturers had taken the products off the market before 
thursdays expanded recall the council said 
