more than 400 ethnic albanian 
teenagers were hospitalized thursday in podujevo a town in 
restive kosovo province after being felled by a mysterious illness 
that officials said may be poison 
official radio belgrade said about 4000 ethnic albanians 
gathered in the streets of podujevo upon hearing the news some of 
