at a recent meeting with video 
industry analysts blockbuster entertainment corp executives 
passed out free cinderella tapes 
the symbolism was subtle yet clear for those familiar with 
blockbusters chief who went from the unglamorous world of trash 
collection to the glitz of the movie industry and quickly 
transformed an obscure group of video stores into the nations top 
chain 
were not twice as smart we just work twice as hard said 
h wayne huizenga blockbuster chairman and chief executive 
officer weve only been at it for three years id say thats 
not too bad 
