copy kochs famous line how am i doin huizenga prefers to 
let numbers tell the story 
since huizenga purchased blockbuster for less than 19 million 
from a dallasbased video retailer the chain has grown from 19 to 
nearly 1200 outlets from guam to england at the present rate an 
average of one new blockbuster store opens a day and huizenga 
predicts sales could top 1 billion this year 
although blockbusters aggressive expansion has led to concern 
by some industry analysts huizenga believes the pace is 
manageable about 160 of the nearly 400 stores opened by 
blockbuster last year were companyowned the rest were franchise 
operators who need little if any help in getting started he said 
so thats really about one store every other day were 
directly responsible for its fast but not unreasonable said 
huizenga 
