where land was valued at 7500 per square foot the report said 
the land agency said residential land prices in tokyo slipped an 
average of 03 percent last year but commercial land prices in the 
capital rose 17 percent 
the report was based on a survey of land prices conducted jan 1 
at 16865 spots across the country the agency said 
