by 3 million merchants worldwide is looking hard at ways to learn 
more about the competition 
obviously the american market is an attractive place said 
bruce brittain head of brittain associates inc an atlantabased 
consulting firm that does market research on creditcard use 
theyre targeting people with the big bucks 
